---
title: Double Spiced Gravy Chicken & Cheesy Parsnip Mash  with Garlic Veggies
description: Want an easy way to make dinner a little more interesting without having to add a tone of spices and extra ingredients? We highly recommend a gravy to drizzle over the chicken and a punch of garlic for the veggies. Soak it up with a fluffy and cheesy parsnip mash and dinner has reached a new level of tastiness.

*Unfortunately, this
week's silverbeet was in
short supply, so we've
replaced it with baby
spinach. Don't worry,
the recipe will be just as
delicious, just be sure to
follow your recipe card!*
